Level 2: The Pharaoh's "Smart Palace"

Location: The Temple of Luxor
Background: Kobayashi accidentally enters the pharaoh's palace, only to find it equipped with electric lights and strange music.

Unreasonable items:

Smart speaker (playing pop music) — The Sanctuary is playing "Shape of You.".

LED pendant lights—modern lighting flickers on the ceiling.

Tablet — The priestess uses a tablet to record the sacrificial list.

Plot points:
The pharaoh mistakenly believed these were "gifts from the gods." After Xiao Lin explained, he turned off the power, and energy fragments appeared behind the tablet
